[0.000, "o", "Overridable: false\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "Why: The manifest domain must match the name of the integration directory under custom_components/. A mismatch causes Home Assistant to silently misidentify the integration, breaking HACS discovery \r\nand core platform loading. Note: this rule cannot be overridden via hasscheck.yaml.\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "Source: \u001b[4;94mhttps://developers.home-assistant.io/docs/creating_integration_manifest\u001b[0m\r\n"]
